reviewText: Too much time promoting her own runs and her sponsors.

I was very disappointed with this video.  All it shows is Kim roping over and over - maybe showing others rope and what they are doing wrong would have help, but just to watch Kim who obviously knows how to rope didn't help me.  It doesn't really teach you anything...ie nothing on ropes to use, breakaway hondos to use in practice, the correct way to swing a rope.  I was just very disappointed.

Helpful DVD, however the "extra movie" at the end was dumb.

Would have liked more information on ropes, different styles, etc.
